OL,3,CWarfare is changing faster than ever,
OL,4,Csays Defence Secretary
OL,6,FWarfare is changing faster than ever
OL,7,Fand our technology must keep up, the
OL,8,FDefence Secretary has said.
OL,10,FSpeaking at Cardiff Castle on
OL,11,FThursday, John Healey stressed the
OL,12,Fimportance of developing new
OL,13,Fautonomous and uncrewed systems, such
OL,14,Fas drones.
OL,16,FHe appeared alongside Welsh Secretary
OL,17,FJo Stevens and First Minister Baroness
OL,18,FEluned Morgan to announce the Wales
OL,19,Fdefence growth deal, which aims to
OL,20,Fmake it easier for small businesses in
OL,21,FWales to secure defence contracts.
