OL,6,FMr Healey said: "The result will be
OL,7,Fmore opportunities for young people in
OL,8,FWales, more jobs for workers in Wales,
OL,9,Fmore investment in businesses in
OL,10,FWales, and more battle-winning
OL,11,Ftechnology made in Wales for our armed
OL,12,Fforces.
OL,14,F"This is a nation which takes great
OL,15,Fpride in our armed forces and with
OL,16,Fvery good reason.
