OL,3,CWarfare is changing faster than ever,
OL,4,Csays Defence Secretary
OL,6,F"We have the finest sailors, pilots
OL,7,Fand soldiers, but the war in Ukraine
OL,8,Fnow reminds us of this hard truth that
OL,9,Fan armed forces is only as strong as
OL,10,Fthe industry and the innovators that
OL,11,Fstand by.
OL,13,F"Technology is changing the nature of
OL,14,Fwarfare faster now than at any time in
OL,15,Fhistory.
OL,17,F"So, developing uncrewed digital
OL,18,Ftechnology is not just an optional
OL,19,Fextra, it's absolutely essential for
OL,20,Four own future defence."
