OL,6,F"Through this deal, we want to set out
OL,7,Fto begin the process of onshoring
OL,8,Ftheir production here in the UK, here
OL,9,Fin Wales," he added.
OL,11,F"And in turn, ensuring that the war-
OL,12,Ffighting readiness of our own armed
OL,13,Fforces and those of our Nato allies
OL,14,Fwill be secure for years to come."
OL,16,FAs part of the #50 million deal, a new
OL,17,Fdefence technical excellence college
OL,18,Fis expected to open next year, in
OL,19,Forder to train more engineers in Wales.
